    public abstract class WorkSpaceViewElement
extends javafx.scene.layout.StackPane
    Abstract class from which all widgets used to represent WorkSpaceGraphElement in the WorkSpaceGraphView will descend.

      • transform

        public void transform(double deltaX,
                      double deltaY,
                      TransformerLocation location)
        This function is responsible for collecting information from a TransformSpot, and figuring out what might have to be resized, then sending the message to its element. This function should intercept the signal if this node cannot be resized! *******NOTE::: This calculation is done using a coordinate plane that increases in the right, down directions.
        Parameters:
        deltaX - : The amount that the mouse moved in the x-coordinate plane. negative if the mouse moved to the left, positive if it moved to the right.
        deltaY - : The amount that the mouse moved in the y-coordinate plane. negative if the mouse moved to the left, positive if it moved to the right.
        location - : The TransformSpot that generated this event.
